ain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_Twists_and_Turns_on_the_Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_NARA_-_7722303.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/85/Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_View_from_Pulloff_on_Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_NARA_-_7722299.jpg/1280px-Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_View_from_Pulloff_on_Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_NARA_-_7722299.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/85/Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_View_from_Pulloff_on_Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_NARA_-_7722299.jpg","cap":"Talladega Scenic Drive View from Pulloff on Talladega Scenic Drive","desc":"Mist lies gently over the rolling, forested hills seen from a pulloff on the Talladega Scenic Drive. Location: Along Talledega Scenic Drive, Alabama (33.641° N 85.628° W) Status: Public domain. Photo by Joe Watts","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_View_from_Pulloff_on_Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_NARA_-_7722299.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d3/Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_Winding_through_the_Talladega_National_Forest_-_NARA_-_7722298.jpg/1280px-Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_Winding_through_the_Talladega_National_Forest_-_NARA_-_7722298.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d3/Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_Winding_through_the_Talladega_National_Forest_-_NARA_-_7722298.jpg","cap":"Talladega Scenic Drive Winding through the Talladega National Forest","desc":"Long early morning shadows greet the visitor on the Talladega Scenic Drive through the Talladega National Forest. Location: Talladega National Forest, Alabama (33.487° N 85.788° W) Status: Public domain.","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Talladega_Scenic_Drive_-_Winding_through_the_Talladega_National_Forest_-_NARA_-_7722298.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/90/Chapter_XI%2C_Volume_7_-_Post_Office_Department_-_Mail_Contracts%2C_Alabama%2C_Georgia%2C_and_Mississippi%2C_1861_-_1862_-_DPLA_-_01486ee09169df26c6766525934c0511_%28page_281%29.jpg/1280px-thumbnail.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/90/Chapter_XI%2C_Volume_7_-_Post_Office_Department_-_Mail_Contracts%2C_Alabama%2C_Georgia%2C_and_Mississippi%2C_1861_-_1862_-_DPLA_-_01486ee09169df26c6766525934c0511_%28page_281%29.jpg","cap":"Chapter XI, Volume 7 Post Office Department Mail Contracts, Alabama, G","desc":"This volume contains contracts to transport the mail on specified mail routes in Alabama, Georgia, and Mississippi. The majority of the contracts were for routes in Alabama. Each contract is a printed fill-in-the blank form that indicates the route number, date of contract, amount to be paid the contractor, name of contractor, sureties, terms of the contract, and description of the route, which we","credit":"War Department. The Adjutant General's Office. War Records O · Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Chapter_XI,_Volume_7_-_Post_Office_Department_-_Mail_Contracts,_Alabama,_Georgia,_and_Mississippi,_1861_-_1862_-_DPLA_-_01486ee09169df26c6766525934c0511_(page_281).jpg"}]}